DANCING WITH THE STARS 2019 NEWS ON SEASON 29 CAST AND EPISODES

Youthful in yellow! Dancing With The Stars vet Julianne Hough stands out in a sharp suit... after she 'agreed to the terms of divorce' with Brooks Laich Julianne Hough looked like she had a spring in her step on Tuesday as she wore a bright yellow suit from St John in New York City. The Dancing With The Stars veteran resembles a top runway fashion model as she included two very high end accessories: Gianvito Rossi shoes and a Bottega Veneta handbag that was held on one hip. This appearance comes just weeks after she signed off papers that will lead to the divorce from husband Brooks Laich, a former hockey player....read Julianne Hough stands out in NYC

Olivia Jade dazzles in green for cover of The House magazine.. as she chats about criticism: 'I am a pretty sensitive human' Olivia Jade is the cover star of The House Magazine's Art and Entertainment issue. She wore a green three-piece co-ord for the cover of the publication, showing off her impeccable style. Olivia Jade graces the cover of The House Magazine

Julianne Hough looks ready for spring in flowing dress as she arrives at Good Morning America to talk up her special Step Into... The Movies Julianne Hough looked ready for spring as she arrived for an early appearance on Good Morning America in New York, outfitted in a flowing ankle length dress. Julianne Hough looks ready for spring in flowing dress

DWTS pro Brandon Armstrong announces engagement to girlfriend Brylee Ivers: 'I'm just so excited for our future together!' The DWTS pro revealed that he popped the question to his ladylove on Monday and presented her with a custom 3.5-carat engagement ring. DWTS pro Brandon Armstrong announces engagement to Brylee Ivers

Brian Austin Green's pregnant DWTS girlfriend Sharna doesn't compare herself to his ex-wife Megan Fox: 'She is her own self and an amazing woman' Sharna Burgess shared her thoughts on comparing herself to her boyfriend Brian Austin Green's ex-wife Megan Fox. A fan asked her, 'How do you deal with following in Megan Fox's footsteps?' Sharna Burgess says that she doesn't compare herself to Megan Fox

Missy Keating puts on a very leggy display in black denim minidress as she leaves a party in Dublin The model, 21, stunned as she stepped out in a short black denim dress that had lace up detailing on the sides to cinch her in at her svelte waist. Missy Keating puts on a very leggy display in black denim minidress

Maksim Chmerkovskiy leans on wife Peta Murgatroyd back home in Los Angeles while dealing with 'shame' of fleeing war in Ukraine after escaping to Poland He is home safe in Los Angeles after fleeing the war in Ukraine and Maksim Chmerkovsky, 42, appears to be leaning on his wife Peta Murgatroyd, 35, for support as he processes the trauma. Maksim Chmerkovskiy leans on Peta Murgatroyd after fleeing Ukraine war

Dancing With The Stars alum Cheryl Burke says exploring her mental health after filing for divorce from Matthew Lawrence has been 'scary' The 37-year-old dancer, who filed for divorce from Matthew Lawrence after almost three years of marriage in February, has been learning about 'how the brain works' since the split. Cheryl Burke says that she has been 'learning how the brain works'

EXCLUSIVE: DWTS pro Maksim Chmerkovskiy pictured in Malibu after emotional reunion with wife Peta Murgatroyd and his 'traumatic' escape from war-torn Ukraine Maksim Chmerkovskiy has was pictured in Malibu on Wednesday, just hours after he arrived home in Los Angeles after a 'traumatic' escape from war-torn Ukraine. DWTS pro Maksim Chmerkovskiy pictured in Malibu

Safe at last! DWTS pro Maksim Chmerkovskiy arrives back in LA to emotional welcome from wife Peta Murgatroyd after 'traumatic' escape from war-torn Ukraine The couple shared an emotional hug as Maks ended a harrowing journey that took him from Kyiv, the capital of Ukraine, to Warsaw in Poland and then on to America. Maksim Chmerkovskiy arrives in LA to emotional welcome from wife Peta

Cheryl Burke is seen without her wedding ring for the first time as she walks her dog in LA... after filing for divorce from Matthew Lawrence The Dancing With The Stars pro, 37, was not wearing her wedding band as she strolled through the hills in Los Angeles with her beloved French bulldog. Cheryl Burke is seen without her wedding ring for the first time

Dancing With The Stars pro Maksim Chmerkovskiy boards a flight to LA...after dramatic ordeal fleeing war-torn Ukraine amid Russian invasion He reached Warsaw, Poland on Tuesday after fleeing his war-torn native Ukraine amid the Russian invasion. Dancing With The Stars pro Maksim Chmerkovskiy boards a flight to LA

Cheryl Burke reflects on her split from Matthew Lawrence with solo trip to their wedding venue... after filing for divorce after two years of marriage The 37-year-old DWTS pro basked in the sunlight while standing on a balcony at the Fairmont Grand Del Mar, the same place she said her vows to Lawrence, 42, in May 2019 when they were married. Cheryl Burke reflects on divorce with solo trip to her wedding venue

Dancing With The Stars pro Maksim Chmerkovskiy reaches Poland after 31 hours of no sleep on 'traumatizing' train ride with women and children fleeing Russian invasion Maksim Chmerkovskiy has reached Poland. The Dancing With The Stars pro has been documenting his journey fleeing his native country after the Russian invasion. Maksim Chmerkovskiy reaches Poland after 31 hours of no sleep

Maksim Chmerkovskiy's wife Peta Murgatroyd admits she's going through 'hell' while he's in Ukraine and thanks people for support Murgatroyd, 35, took to Instagram on Sunday with an emotional message in which she shared that an empathetic group of strangers had made a kind gesture to her amid the absence of her husband. Maksim Chmerkovskiy's wife Peta Murgatroyd going through 'hell'

DWTS pro Maksim Chmerkovskiy says he's 'safe' in a bomb shelter in Ukraine while 'Kyiv is under serious attack'... as he shares haunting footage of explosions lighting up the city The 42-year-old Dancing With The Stars pro paced around an underground parking garage serving as a bomb shelter as Russian forces continued the attack around him in Ukraine's capital Kyiv. DWTS' Maksim Chmerkovskiy is 'safe' in bomb shelter in Ukraine

Matthew Lawrence shows off his bare ring finger as he steps out after Cheryl Burke divorce filing without his wedding band The Brotherly Love actor, 42, was not wearing his wedding band when he was spotted driving around Los Angeles on Friday. Matthew Lawrence ditches his wedding band following Cheryl Burke split

Dancing With The Stars vet Julianne Hough and hockey player Brooks Laich 'agree to the terms of their divorce'... almost two years after their split The 33-year-old former Dancing with the Stars professional and judge filed for divorce from the 38-year-old star in 2020, six months after they confirmed their split. Julianne Hough and Brooks Laich 'agree to the terms of their divorce'

DWTS pro Cheryl Burke speaks out for the first time after filing for divorce from husband Matthew Lawrence The 37-year-old Dancing with the Stars professional asked for 'understanding' and 'privacy' as she navigated the difficult time in her life following the end of her relationship with the actor. Cheryl Burke speaks out after filing for divorce from Matthew Lawrence

'S**t's going down': DWTS pro Maksim Chmerkovskiy breaks down in tears during emotional videos from Kyiv following Russian invasion of Ukraine ... as he takes to 'a bomb shelter' for safety Ukrainian-born Dancing With the Stars pro Maksim Chmerkovskiy is fearing for his life and the lives of his friends in Kiev following a Russian invasion into the country over night. Maksim Chmerkovskiy in tears during emotional videos from Kyiv

Dancing with the Stars pro Cheryl Burke files for divorce from husband Matthew Lawrence after two years of marriage Cheryl reportedly cited 'irreconcilable differences' as the reason for the split, and the pair are said to have a prenuptial agreement in place. DWTS pro Cheryl Burke files for divorce from Matthew Lawrence

Missy Keating looks sensational in figure-hugging red dress and faux fur coat as she celebrates her 21st birthday following Dancing With The Stars elimination The model appeared in good spirits as she was joined by her brother Jack and several friends at trendy venue House. Missy Keating looks sensational as she celebrates her 21st birthday

Nikki Bella shares that fiancé Artem Chigvintsev continues to battle pneumonia after he left Dancing with the Stars tour due to the lung infection Nikki Bella confirmed that her fiancé Artem Chigvintsev is still battling pneumonia, four weeks after finding out he had the lung infection. Nikki Bella shares that Artem Chigvintsev is still battling pneumonia

Julianne Hough is effortlessly chic in an oversized blazer and mid-calf suede boots as she glams up for the Sports Illustrated Super Bowl party in LA Showing off her enviable style in an oversized blazer and mid-calf suede boots, the two-time Dancing With The Stars winner, 34, knew how to pose up a storm for the cameras. Julianne Hough is effortlessly chic in an oversized blazer and boots

Amanda Kloots is the picture of a doting mom during a day on the beach with son Elvis in Malibu... and has chance meeting with Bob Saget's widow Kelly Rizzo Amanda Kloots was the picture of a doting mom during a day on the beach with son Elvis in Malibu, which included a chance meeting with Bob Saget's widow Kelly Rizzo. Amanda Kloots takes son Elvis to the beach and meets Bob Saget's widow

Artem Chigvintsev reveals he's still battling pneumonia after leaving Dancing with the Stars tour due to health issues Artem, who welcomed his first son into the world with fiance Nikki Bella in 2020, was optimistic that another round of antibiotics would help finally curb his on-going illness. Artem Chigvintsev still battling pneumonia after leaving DWTS tour

Artem Chigvintsev, 39, taking a break from DWTS tour to attend to 'some unexpected health issues' Artem Chigvintsev, 39, announced he is taking a temporary break from the current DWTS tour to attend to 'some unexpected health issues.' Artem Chigvintsev taking a break from DWTS tour due to 'health issues'

'I eat pasta and ice cream!': Marie Osmond EXCLUSIVE - The star, 62, reveals how she STILL indulges while keeping off those 50lbs she lost 14 years ago 'I've tried every fad diet out there, they don't work. If you starve yourself, you're going to mess up your metabolism,' she said. She likes to eat ravioli and potstickers, she told DailyMail.com. Marie Osmond STILL indulges in favorite foods after 50lb weight loss

'I've received so much hate': Olympic gymnast Suni Lee reveals she's been attacked by racist trolls for dating a black man after going public with USC football player beau on Instagram Sunisa confirmed she was in a relationship with Jaylin Smith on December 26, but some people in the Hmong American community took issue with her dating a black man. Sunisa Lee trolled for dating black man - after anti-Asian attack

Ronan Keating's daughter Missy, 20, is paired with pro dance partner Ervinas Merfeldas, 19, as DWTS 'hope to shake up show with youngest ever couple' Ronan Keating's daughter Missy is one half of the youngest ever coupling on Dancing With The Stars following her pairing with pro dancer Ervinas Merfeldas. DWTS 'pair youngest ever partnership as in hopes of shaking up show'

Tyra Banks sells her Pacific Palisades home for $7.9 MILLION... after flipping a string of LA properties in recent years Tyra Banks, 48, has sold her Pacific Palisades home for $7.895 million, earning nearly $1 million in profit after putting it on the market in November 2021. Tyra Banks sells her Pacific Palisades home for $7.9 MILLION

Strictly bosses 'considering a pay rise to lure Anton Du Beke back as a dancer ahead of Bruno Tonioli's comeback to the judging panel' The TV star, 55, was part of the judging panel for this year's series as he filled in for Bruno Tonioli who remained in the US as a judge on Dancing With The Stars amid covid restrictions. Anton Du Beke 'could be set for pay rise to return as a dancer'

Bianca Gascoigne sends temperatures soaring in a latex Mrs. Claus outfit before showing off her impressive acrobatic skills as she scoops second place in the final of Italy's Dancing With The Stars Bianca Gascoigne sent temperatures soaring in a skimpy Christmas outfit as she picked up second place in the final of Dancing With The Stars in Italy. Bianca Gascoigne lands 2nd place on Italy's Dancing With The Stars

Bianca Gascoigne sets pulses racing in sizzling black leather lingerie as she flaunts her eye-popping curves in a racy photoshoot The reality star, 34, showcased her incredible figure in black leather lingerie as she posed up a storm in a new racy photoshoot. Bianca Gascoigne showcases her toned physique in sizzling photoshoot

Gleb Savchenko's ex-wife Elena Samodanova requests primary custody of their two children due to his demanding DWTS schedule The former couple - who share daughters Olivia, 11, and Zlata, four - have amicably co-parented since their split last year, with a judge signing off on their divorce in October after 14 years of marriage. Gleb Savchenko's ex wants primary custody of kids due to DWTS schedule

Dancing With The Stars vet Jordan Fisher is expecting his first child, a baby boy, with wife Ellie Woods... a little over a year after getting married Dancing with the Stars Jordan Fisher, 27, announced on his Instagram on Tuesday that he is expecting his first child with his wife Ellie Woods, 23. Jordan and Ellie both posted a Jordan Fisher, 27, is expecting his first child, a boy with his wife

JoJo Siwa becomes the center of attention when she busts out dance moves during break in action of Lakers-Magic game in LA JoJo Siwa became the center of attention when she busted out dance moves during a break in the action of the Lakers-Magic game in LA on Sunday. JoJo Siwa grabs attention by breaking out dance moves at Lakers game

Bianca Gascoigne shows off her toned physique as she strips completely NAKED for racy new photoshoot The reality star, 34, ditched her clothes altogether as she stripped completely naked for what could be her raciest photoshoot yet. Bianca Gascoigne strips completely NAKED for racy new photoshoot

Bianca Gascoigne showcases her taut abs in a cropped activewear set as she leaves Dancing With The Stars rehearsals in Italy Bianca Gascoigne, 35, stepped out in form fitting activewear that showcased her enviable figure after rehearsals at Rai Studios in Rome, Italy. Bianca Gascoigne showcases her taut abs in a cropped activewear set

Olivia Jade shares cheeky photos from Dancing with the Stars as she congratulates winners Iman Shumpert and Daniella Karagach Dancing with the Stars wrapped its 30th season on Monday night. And former candidate Olivia Jade took to Instagram to close out her chapter on the long-running franchise. Olivia Jade shares DWTS photos as she congratulates show's winners

Jojo Siwa continues glamorous roll as she wears glitzy sequin jumpsuit and heels for the SECOND TIME EVER at The View taping...following DWTS loss The 18-year-old television star rocked a glitzy blue sequin jumpsuit as she arrived for a taping of The View in New York City where she spoke about her DWTS loss and newest dance venture Jojo Siwa rocks sequin jumpsuit for The View taping after DWTS loss

Iman Shumpert celebrates his big Mirrorball Trophy win on Dancing With the Stars season 30 alongside second place winner JoJo Siwa DWTS winner Iman Shumpert and his fellow finalists, JoJo Siwa and Amanda Kloots were spotted heading out of Good Morning America on Tuesday. DWTS winner Iman Shumpert out with second place star JoJo Siwa

Mel C looks incredible in gold shimmering gown as she performs at grand finale of Dancing With The Stars The singer, 47, who was eliminated from the show late last month after landing in the bottom two with Olivia Jade, performed the Spice Girls' 2 Become 1 in a tribute to season 30. Mel C performs at grand finale of Dancing With The Stars

Dancing With The Stars: Iman Shumpert and Daniella Karagach win season 30 and Mirrorball Trophy The 31-year-old basketball player and his pro partner Daniella Karagach, 28, won season 30 of Dancing With The Stars on Monday during a two-hour finale on ABC. Dancing With The Stars: Iman Shumpert and Daniella Karagach win trophy

Julianne Hough will step in for brother Derek to judge finale of Dancing With the Stars after he tested positive for breakthrough case of COVID-19 Derek Hough's recent COVID-19 diagnosis threw a wrench into the finals of Dancing With the Stars but luckily his sister will step in for him as a judge. Julianne Hough will judge DWTS finale in place of COVID positive Derek

Gazza good look! Bianca Gascoigne pulls some VERY animated expressions and gives her all on the dancefloor in sexy red bra top and mini skirt on Dancing With The Stars in Italy Bianca Gascoigne sent pulses racing in a red hot bralette and mini skirt combo as performed a sexy routine with partner Simone Di Pascale Bianca Gascoigne sizzles in a bralette on Dancing With The Stars

Amanda Kloots smiles as she arrives at Dancing With The Stars' Los Angeles practice facility...after getting a perfect score while performing to a song written by her late husband Her outing comes just a day after she put on an emotional performance and scored a perfect 40 after dancing to a song written by her late husband on the hit ABC program. Amanda Kloots arrives at Dancing With The Stars' practice facility

JoJo Siwa describes Demi Lovato as 'the sweetest, nicest, kindest people' after the singer asks Dancing With The Stars fans to vote for the teen JoJo Siwa has described Demi Lovato as the 'one of the sweetest, nicest, kindest, and most supportive people ever.' The 18-year-old star was overwhelmed to see her hero show support. JoJo Siwa makes final Dancing With The Stars cut, gushes over Lovato

Battle of the super fans! Peloton devotees go to war with DWTS viewers over criticism of beloved instructor Cody Rigsby after he beat out favorites Suni Lee and Melora Hardin The two groups are feuding over the results of the semifinals, which aired on Monday. Many people were shocked when Cody and his partner, Cheryl Burke, made it to the final round. Peloton fans fight with Dancing With the Stars fans over Cody Rigsby

Derek Hough tests positive for breakthrough case of COVID-19 ahead of the Dancing With the Stars finals: 'I feel strong' Dancing With the Stars judge Derek Hough revealed that he's tested positive for a breakthrough case of COVID-19, in an Instagram post on Tuesday. Derek Hough tests positive for COVID-19 ahead of the DWTS finals

Dancing With The Stars: Amanda Kloots performs emotional dance to late husband's song Live Your Life The 39-year-old co-host of The Talk was saved by the judges after an emotional dance dedicated to her late husband Nick Cordero on Monday's episode of Dancing With The Stars. DWTS: Amanda Kloots performs to late husband's song Live Your Life

Bianca Gascoigne showcases her ample assets in a mini dress as she puts her acrobatic skills to use on Italy's Dancing With The Stars The 34-year-old sent temperatures soaring as she took to the ballroom of Italy's Dancing With The Stars on Saturday night at Auditorium Rai del Foro Italico. Bianca Gascoigne dons a green dress on Italy's Dancing With The Stars

JoJo Siwa, Amanda Kloots and Cheryl Burke bring Dancing with the Stars energy to the Vulture Festival in LA JoJo Siwa, 18, Amanda Kloots, 39, and Cheryl Burke, 37, attended Vulture Festival with their Dancing with the Stars castmates on Saturday. The women were in good spirits for the event. JoJo Siwa, Amanda Kloots and Cheryl Burke attend Vulture Festival

Nikki Bella says she and fiancé Artem Chigvintsev got 'back into therapy' after hitting a 'rough patch': 'Now we're stronger than ever' Nikki Bella, 37, told her twin sister Brie Bella on Wednesday's episode of The Bellas Podcast that she and fiancé Artem Chigvintsev went to therapy after a rough patch in their relationship. Nikki Bella went to therapy with Artem Chigvintsev after 'rough patch'

At least it wasn't for cheating! Olivia Jade gets voted off Dancing With The Stars after performing twice during Janet Jackson Night Olivia Jade, 22, and pro partner Valentin Chmerkovskiy, 35, were eliminated from Dancing With The Stars on Monday during a double elimination episode of the ABC show. Dancing With The Stars: Olivia Jade exits during Janet Jackson Night
